These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, old-henry, dunhill, ritmeester
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, australian, malaysian, thai
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, azure, light-blue, yellow
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, doctor, mechanic, freelancer
 1. the australian is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 2. the old-henry-smoker is the thai##1
 3. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the mechanic is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 5. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the malaysian##1
 9. the accountant is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
11. the person who likes azure is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Cigar    | dunhill   | old-henry       | aristoff | ritmeester   |
| Nationality        | australian    | thai  | malaysian      | italian |
| Color         | yellow      | azure | light-blue         | turquise   |
| Job   | accountant | doctor       | mechanic        | freelancer   |

