.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, tea, cola
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, hedgehog, turtle
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving, collecting, cooking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, rose, marigold
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who growsrose is the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the owner of the goat and the person who growssunflower##2
5. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | mirinda | cola | tea |
| Pet   | cat  | hedgehog | goat         | turtle      |
| Hobby         | collecting      | skydiving    | cooking         | card-games   |
| Flower     | sunflower         | amaryllis    | marigold          | rose         |

