.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
City: marseilles, colone, liverpool, prague
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge, billiard
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, freelancer, social-worker, software-developer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, soy-milk, mirinda
 1. the person playing bridge is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 4. the social-worker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the architect is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person playing scrabble##2
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| City          | colone | prague  | marseilles | liverpool      |
| Game   | go       | billiard    | scrabble      | bridge      |
| Job           | software-developer     | architect     | freelancer         | social-worker   |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | cola | milk     | mirinda |

