.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, bridge, mah-jongg, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, quad-bike, skateboard
House: modern, wooden, ranch-style, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, folk, pop
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
5. the ranch-style house is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of pop##1
8. the person playing canasta is between the fan of punk and the farmhouse house##2
9. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Game           | monopoly     | canasta | bridge | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | subway       | helicopter      | skateboard   |
| House   | wooden   | modern   | farmhouse    | ranch-style       |
| Music-Genre           | punk | disco        | folk    | pop        |

