 8. the person driving the van is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
10. the havana-smoker is between the person driving the train and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
