 6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the owner of the pony is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person eating peas is the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
11. the owner of the rat is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Cigar         | dannemann      | chaman | game       | swisher   |
| Pet   | rat     | mouse | pony | goat |
| City   | miami    | liverpool     | berlin        | new-york       |
| Food     | raspberry | potato   | apricot   | peas       |

