.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, may, april
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, reading, puzzles
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, whist, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, milk, juice
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking cola##2
 5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 6. the person playing domino is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person drinking tea##2
 7. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday          | november | april   | may   | july |
| Hobby           | baking   | reading     | card-games   | puzzles |
| Game   | canasta    | domino    | snooker   | whist   |
| Beverage         | tea    | cola | juice | milk    |

 